    <arm_group_type>Active Comparator</arm_group_type>
    <description>Usual approach for the disease management. Patients in Group B will receive usual education and, at any time during the study duration, if needed, will be instructed on Self Monitoring of Blood Glucose, performed with any glucose meter.</description>
